# AWS credentials for S3 metadata access
# The AWS SDK uses the default credential provider chain.
# For local development with MFA profiles, the `npm run scrape` command
# handles credential export automatically via `aws configure export-credentials`.
#
# For deployment (e.g. Vercel), set these environment variables:
AWS_REGION=ap-southeast-2
# AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=
# AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=
# AWS_SESSION_TOKEN=
